sequenceDiagram
    participant SF as Schema Forge CLI
    participant WH as Etendo Webhooks
    participant DB as ETGO_SF_* Tables
    participant RT as NeoServlet (Runtime)

    Note over SF: After curation is complete

    SF->>WH: SFUpsertSpec(windowId, name, type)
    WH->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE ETGO_SF_SPEC
    DB-->>WH: spec_id

    SF->>WH: SFPopulateSpec(spec_id)
    WH->>DB: Auto-create ETGO_SF_ENTITY + ETGO_SF_FIELD from AD metadata
    DB-->>WH: entities + fields created

    loop For each curated field
        SF->>WH: SFUpsertField(entity_id, column, isIncluded, isReadOnly)
        WH->>DB: UPDATE ETGO_SF_FIELD
    end

    Note over RT: No restart needed — config is live

    RT->>DB: Read ETGO_SF_* on each request
    DB-->>RT: Current config
    RT->>RT: Serve filtered API based on config
